<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>关于我 - 后台管理</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="admin-layout">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="sidebar-header">
        <a href="/" class="admin-brand-mark gradient-button" aria-label="Poppis">
          <span class="gradient-text">Poppis</span>
        </a>
        <div>
          <p class="admin-kicker">Content Studio</p>
          <h2>后台管理</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <nav class="sidebar-nav">
        <a href="/poppis-console/dashboard" class="nav-item">仪表盘</a>
        <a href="/poppis-console/posts" class="nav-item">文章管理</a>
        <a href="/poppis-console/categories" class="nav-item">分类管理</a>
        <a href="/poppis-console/tags" class="nav-item">标签管理</a>
        <a href="/poppis-console/about" class="nav-item active">关于我</a>
        <a href="/poppis-console/logout" class="nav-item logout">退出登录</a>
      </nav>
    </aside>

    <main class="admin-main">
      <div class="admin-header">
        <div>
          <p class="admin-kicker">Profile Page</p>
          <h1>关于我页面管理</h1>
          <p class="admin-lead">这一页会直接影响读者对作者的第一印象，建议持续维护，而不是一次性写完。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-card">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <p class="admin-kicker">Edit</p>
            <h2>编辑关于我页面</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <form method="POST" action="/poppis-console/about" class="post-form">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="content">页面内容 (支持 HTML)</label>
            <textarea id="content" name="content" rows="20" required><%= about.content %></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-actions">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">保存</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
